<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"  TextAlignment="Justify"   xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph>Essential Presentation library has support for inserting and editing connectors in a PowerPoint presentation.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>This sample demonstrates how to insert the connectors in a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph>
<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}"><Bold>Features:</Bold></TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>
<Paragraph>
This sample demonstrates the following features:
</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Support for 'Straight', 'Bent', and 'Curve' connectors in a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Support for different connector arrow styles.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Support to insert, edit, remove, clone, and convert connectors.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph><Bold>Note:</Bold> This library supports creating, editing, and converting of connectors for .pptx format alone.</Paragraph>

